@baseUrl = http://localhost:3004/api/auth
@listingsUrl = http://localhost:3005/api/listings
@token = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOjMsImVtYWlsIjoidGVzdHVzZXIxMjNAZXhhbXBsZS5jb20iLCJ1c2VybmFtZSI6bnVsbCwiaWF0IjoxNzcyNTg4MjIyLCJleHAiOjE3NzMxOTMwMjJ9.Phh7ZtwWsUe4Hhxbyw_D4sGhTQ5uflDJMSLmaSUQxqo

### ============================================
### SETUP: LOGIN & CREATE LISTING
### ============================================

### 1. Create User  (copy the access_token)
POST http://localhost:3004/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testuser123@example.com",
  "password": "Test1234"
}


### 1. Login (copy the access_token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "identifier": "testuser123@example.com",
  "password": "Test1234"
}

### 2. Create a listing first (copy the listing id)
POST {{listingsUrl}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Test Apartment for Photo Upload",
  "location": "Paris 13e",
  "price": 650,
  "currency": "EUR",
  "availableDate": "2026-04-01",
  "spotsTotal": 2,
  "spotsFilled": 0,
  "description": "Testing photo upload functionality",
  "hasWifi": true,
  "hasKitchen": true,
  "hasLaundry": false,
  "hasMetroNearby": true,
  "hasGarden": false,
  "hasParking": true,
  "petsOK": false,
  "hasGym": false,
  "hasAC": true,
  "isSecure": true
}

### ============================================
### UPLOAD LISTING PHOTOS
### ============================================

### 3. Upload 2 Photos (Minimum) ✅
POST {{listingsUrl}}/1/photos
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="photo1.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< /home/younesoun/Downloads/test1.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="photo2.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< /home/younesoun/Downloads/test2.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### 4. Upload 3 More Photos (Total will be 5) ✅
POST {{listingsUrl}}/1/photos
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="photo3.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< /path/to/your/photo3.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="photo4.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< /path/to/your/photo4.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="photo5.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< /path/to/your/photo5.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### 5. Upload 1 More Photo (Total will be 6 - Maximum) ✅
POST {{listingsUrl}}/1/photos
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="photo6.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< /path/to/your/photo6.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

