### ============================================
### GET LISTING (VERIFY PHOTOS)
### ============================================

### 12. Get Listing Details (check images array)
GET {{listingsUrl}}/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 13. Get All Listings (see photos in list)
GET {{listingsUrl}}/all

### 14. Get My Listings (verify your listing has photos)
GET {{listingsUrl}}/my-listings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### DELETE PHOTOS
### ============================================

### 15. Delete Photo at Index 0 (first photo) ✅
DELETE {{listingsUrl}}/1/photos/0
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 16. Delete Photo at Index 2 (third photo in array) ✅
DELETE {{listingsUrl}}/1/photos/2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 17. Delete Last Photo ✅
DELETE {{listingsUrl}}/1/photos/5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 18. Delete Invalid Index (Should FAIL - 400) ❌
DELETE {{listingsUrl}}/1/photos/99
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 19. Delete Photo Without Token (Should FAIL - 401) ❌
DELETE {{listingsUrl}}/1/photos/0

### 20. Try to Delete When Only 2 Photos Left (Should FAIL) ❌
# First make sure listing has exactly 2 photos
# Then try to delete one (should fail because minimum is 2)
DELETE {{listingsUrl}}/1/photos/0
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### DELETE PHOTOS - OTHER USER'S LISTING
### ============================================

### 21. Create Second User & Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "seconduser@example.com",
  "password": "Test1234"
}

###
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "identifier": "seconduser@example.com",
  "password": "Test1234"
}

### 22. Try to Upload Photos to First User's Listing (Should FAIL - 403) ❌
# Use second user's token
POST {{listingsUrl}}/1/photos
Authorization: Bearer SECOND_USER_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="photo1.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< /path/to/your/photo1.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="photo2.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< /path/to/your/photo2.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### 23. Try to Delete Photos from First User's Listing (Should FAIL - 403) ❌
DELETE {{listingsUrl}}/1/photos/0
Authorization: Bearer SECOND_USER_TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================
### COMPLETE WORKFLOW
### ============================================

### 24. WORKFLOW: Create Listing → Upload Photos → View → Delete One
###

# Step 1: Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "identifier": "testuser123",
  "password": "Test1234"
}

###
# Step 2: Create listing (copy ID from response)
POST {{listingsUrl}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Workflow Test Apartment",
  "location": "Casablanca",
  "price": 5000,
  "currency": "MAD",
  "availableDate": "2026-05-01",
  "spotsTotal": 1,
  "spotsFilled": 0,
  "description": "Complete workflow test",
  "hasWifi": true,
  "hasKitchen": true,
  "hasLaundry": true,
  "hasMetroNearby": false,
  "hasGarden": false,
  "hasParking": false,
  "petsOK": true,
  "hasGym": false,
  "hasAC": true,
  "isSecure": true
}

###
# Step 3: Upload 3 photos
POST {{listingsUrl}}/LISTING_ID_HERE/photos
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="photo1.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< /path/to/your/photo1.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="photo2.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< /path/to/your/photo2.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="photo3.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< /path/to/your/photo3.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

###
# Step 4: Get listing to see photos
GET {{listingsUrl}}/LISTING_ID_HERE

###
# Step 5: Delete one photo
DELETE {{listingsUrl}}/LISTING_ID_HERE/photos/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
# Step 6: Verify photo was deleted
GET {{listingsUrl}}/LISTING_ID_HERE